title: adguard_5.7+Crack
description:
List of features in this version

+ Adguard now use new network filtration driver
No more redirect, no more conflicts with other software.

+ All conflicts Adguard has with other software are now resolved
+ Complete filtration of browsers in Modern UI mode (Adguard 5.6 did not filter Modern UI if Avast or Kaspersky is installed)
+ HTTPS filtration
- Proxy mode is for backward compatibility only. We plan to remove it in Adguard 6.0.
* Lot of bug fixes
